_sText:
Gg_Ag_Arena By dF_UbeR

This is a small Gun Game project I have been working on for a few days. There are 20 spawn points for each team.  Have fun!

The zip file includes the .bsp with everything packed inside and a .nav file for the map.

Also, if you wouldn't mind, please tell me the ip of your server if you plan on running it. I would like to try the map out with opponents other than bots.

Thanks.
